import React,{useState} from 'react'
import { Box, Typography, Grid, Paper } from '@mui/material'
import HelpOutlinedIcon from '@mui/icons-material/HelpOutlined';


export const Details = () => {

  const [value,setValue]= useState({
   accname: '',
   code:'',
   type:'',
   description:'',
  })

  return (
    <Box >
      <Grid container justifyContent={'center'}>
        <Grid item xs={4} md={6} sx={{ marginTop: 3, boxShadow: 'rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35) 0px 5px 15px' }}>
          <Paper
            sx={{ padding: '17px', height: 'fit-content', marginLeft: '7px' }}
          >
            <form>
              <Typography sx={{ fontSize: '20px' }}>Create Account</Typography>
              <Box>
                <label>
                  <Typography mt={5} mb={1} sx={{ fontSize: "16px", color: "#BD4C46" }}>
                    Account Name
                  </Typography>
                </label>

                <input
                  type='text'
                  value={value.name}
                  onChange={(e) => setValue({...value, name: e.target.accname})}
                  style={{ height: '30px', width: '250px' }}
                />
              </Box>

              <Box>
                <label>
                  <Typography mt={3} mb={1} sx={{ fontSize: "16px", }}>
                    Account Code <HelpOutlinedIcon sx={{ height: '18px', position: 'absolute', marginTop: '2px' }} />
                  </Typography>
                </label>

                <input
                  type='text'
                  value={value.code}
                  onChange={(e) => setValue({...value, code: e.target.code})}
                  style={{ height: '30px', width: '250px' }}
                />
              </Box>

              <Box>
                <label>
                  <Typography mt={3} mb={1} sx={{ fontSize: "16px", color: "#BD4C46" }}>
                    Account Type
                  </Typography>
                </label>
                 <select  value={value.type}  onChange={(e) => setValue({...value, type: e.target.type})} style={{ height: '40px', width: '255px' }}>
                 <option>Stock</option>
                  <option>Customer</option>
                 </select>  
             {/* <Box>
             <TextField select  sx={{  width: '255px' }}>
                <MenuItem >
                <MenuItem ><option>Stock</option></MenuItem>
                 <option>Dealer</option>
                </MenuItem>
        
              </TextField></Box> */}
              </Box>

              <Box>
                <label>
                  <Typography
                    mt={3}
                    mb={1}
                    sx={{ fontSize: "16px", color: "#000" }}
                  >
                    Description
                  </Typography>
                </label>

                <textarea
                  rows={3}
                  cols={25}
                  placeholder="Max 500 characters"
                  value={value.description}
                  onChange={(e) => setValue({...value, description: e.target.description})}
                  style={{
                    padding: "10px",
                    borderRadius: "2px",
                    border: "1px solid gray",
                    fontFamily: 'sans-serif',
                    fontSize: '15px'
                  }}
                />
              </Box>

              <Box>
                <Typography mt={3}><input type="checkbox" ></input>
                  <label style={{ fontFamily: 'inherit', marginLeft: '5px' }}>Add to the watchlist on my dashboard</label></Typography>
              </Box>

              <Box mt={6} >
                <button style={{ height: '40px', width: '65px', backgroundColor: '#CF4B28', color: 'white', border: '1px solid #CF4B28', borderRadius: '5px', fontWeight: 'bold' }} 
                 >Save</button>
                <button style={{ height: '40px', width: '65px', marginLeft: '11px', backgroundColor: 'lightgrey', border: '1px solid lightgray', borderRadius: '5px' }}>Cancel</button>
              </Box>



            </form>
          </Paper>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>

    </Box>
  )
}
